OL,3,CBoy, 4, suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries after hit-and-run
OL,6,FA four-year-old boy remains in
OL,7,Fhospital in a life-threatening
OL,8,Fcondition following a hit-and-run in
OL,9,Fthe Lawrence Weston area of Bristol on
OL,10,FSunday 17 November.
OL,12,FAn 18-year-old man arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of causing serious injury by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving and driving whilst
OL,15,Funfit through drink or drugs remains
OL,16,Fin police custody.
OL,18,FIt follows a collision on Long Cross,
OL,19,Fnear its junction with Kings Weston
OL,20,FRoad, shortly before 2pm.
