OL,3,CBoy, 4, suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries after hit-and-run
OL,6,FPolice were called at 1.51pm following
OL,7,Fa report that a BMW car had left the
OL,8,Froad and collided with the boy.
OL,10,FHe was taken to hospital where he
OL,11,Fremains in a life-threatening
OL,12,Fcondition. His family are being
OL,13,Fsupported by specially trained
OL,14,Fofficers.
OL,16,FIt was also reported that the two
OL,17,Foccupants of the car had left the
OL,18,Fscene.
