OL,3,CBoy, 4, suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries after hit-and-run
OL,6,FA man was arrested on suspicion of
OL,7,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving and driving whilst unfit
OL,9,Fthrough drink or drugs later that
OL,10,Fafternoon. He remains in police
OL,11,Fcustody.
OL,13,FOfficers are keen to speak to a woman
OL,14,Fwho was described as white with blonde
OL,15,Fhair. She was wearing a black puffer
OL,16,Fcoat, blue jeans and light-coloured
OL,17,Fshoes.
