OL,3,CBoy, 4, suffers life-threatening
OL,4,Cinjuries after hit-and-run
OL,6,FNeighbourhood inspector Serena
OL,7,FSerjeant said: "This was a shocking
OL,8,Fcollision and our thoughts remain with
OL,9,Fthe young boy and his family at this
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,F"Understandably, this incident has
OL,13,Fcaused concern in the Lawrence Weston
OL,14,Fcommunity and I'd like to assure
OL,15,Feveryone that a full and thorough
OL,16,Finvestigation is already well underway.
OL,18,F"I would urge anyone who has any
OL,19,Ffootage of the collision or any other
OL,20,Finformation about it which could help,
OL,21,Fto contact us."
